   the console is pretty much   
    all you have available.     

00:20:23,723 --> 00:20:24,505
     And I'll tell you why.     

00:20:25,291 --> 00:20:26,424
       We don't know what       
       you're evaluating        

00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:28,793
