00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:07,231
       It can be any URL.       

00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,917
    The Web Inspector really    
     doesn't take it other      

00:21:12,038 --> 00:21:13,321
      than to get the name      
         at this point.         

00:21:14,607 --> 00:21:16,040
