    do in a normal debugger,    

00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,660
    in addition to hovering     
         over variables         

00:26:37,163 --> 00:26:39,030
      to see their current      
    value or evaluate things    

00:26:40,900 --> 00:26:42,617
     in this current scope      
        in the console.         

